title: Episode 366: No Grip (Feat. dvsn)
itunes:title: Episode 366: No Grip (Feat. dvsn)
description:
Daniel Daley and Nineeten85 of R&B group, dvsn, join the ladies of Lip Service this week to break down their latest hit song, "If I Get Caught." The guys do a great job explaining the single but the ladies obviously have their questions regarding the tracks toxicity. During this episode we also discuss a range of topics including loose vaginas, being eskimos bro's, porn addictions, and much more. Daniel even tells a story about the time he woke up with a knife to his back...enjoy!
